Project: MDZ (MVP)

Goal

- Minimal markdown editor/viewer with filesystem storage. TDD only for necessary paths.

Tech

- Backend: Fastify + local storage; routes `/pages/*`; production alias `/api/pages/*`.
- Frontend: Vite + React + Tailwind; Sidebar/Viewer/Editor. MDX via `@mdx-js/mdx` evaluate with `useDynamicImport: false`.
  - Responsive: sidebar hidden on small screens with a toggle; desktop shows sidebar by default.

Storage

- Plain markdown files (no front-matter/metadata). Title = basename of path.
- Page without children: `PageName.md`. When first child is added, convert to folder: `PageName/README.md` and child `PageName/Child.md`. When last child is removed, convert back to `PageName.md`.
